HOW TO APPLY THIS PATCH
-----------------------
1. Make sure you have a plain vanilla ROM 2.4b2 straight out of box!
   Copy the files in /src directory to a temporary working directory.

2. Extract the archive to the working directory
	gunzip rom24mp.tar.gz
	tar xvf rom24mp.tar

3. Execute patch < mobprog.patch which will patch the original source files.

4. Copy all new and changed files back to ROM 2.4b2 /src directory and
   re-make the source.

5. Insert SURRENDER.HLP to help.are file in /area directory.

